//- ==================

//-
  The `icon` mixin lets us put out a Bootstrap3 icon with all the proper classes.
  e.g. use `+icon('star')` in your views (or other mixins).
mixin icon(kind, classes)
  i.glyphicon(class="glyphicon-#{kind} #{classes || ''}")

//-
  The `starred_level` mixin renders a quizâ€™s difficulty level (a positive number)
  as the relevant number of stars, using Bootstrap3 star icons.
mixin starred_level(quiz)
  - for (var i = 0; i < quiz.level; ++i)
    +icon('star')

